descript.abstract: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Waukesha County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waukesha_Zoning_2014.gdb.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement where applicable. The data for this layer was published with multiple feature classes, and the metadata was generated from the "Waukesha_Zoning_2014" layer.
